rep_input: Patient HR+/HER2- progressed after CDK4/6; what key label-based caveats should I discuss?
model_output: For HR+/HER2- patients progressed after CDK4/6, label-based options depend on prior endocrine and chemo exposure, performance status, and presence of visceral disease.
